Class LibraryCatalog

java.lang.Object
  dxf2svg.util.DatabaseContainer
      dxf2svg.LibraryCatalog
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class LibraryCatalog
extends DatabaseContainer

This class is a wrapper class to implement namespaces for FigureSheetDatabases (see DatabaseContainer for more details. This is important because the FigureSheetDatabase just maintains a table for each figure number and an entry for every sheet. We need to be able to store these values by book as well so we can store multipule instances of Figure 1-1, one for each book. Further when we output the database to XML we need to be able to populate the <Book> tag with its appropriate book attribute value.
